<item>
            <title>[LU-4573] sanityn test_76 fails on DNE (512 != 2048 open files)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4573</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Di Wang &amp;lt;di.wang@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2397a63c-8b65-11e3-a5ce-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/2397a63c-8b65-11e3-a5ce-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems the test needs to fix with striped dir.&lt;br/&gt;
The sub-test test_76 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;512 != 2048 open files&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanityn 76&lt;/p&gt;</description>
